     <TD BGCOLOR="#2E4460"><TEXTAREA NAME="message" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">The default is to open at the same size when it was closed ... don't use the X in the corner to close the window ... use File / Close (or exit) and that should set the screen locators to the proper settings.

Also, minimize all windows exceot that new one, then right click on the start bar and tile them Horizontaly ... that will maximise it AND set the locators too... again, don't use the X to close it, use File / Close.

